<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idca913cd3-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598" identifier="/us/usc/t43/s2408"><num value="2408">§ 2408.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="idca913cd4-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598" identifier="/us/usc/t43/s2408/a"><num value="a" class="bold">(a)</num><heading class="bold"> In general</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There is authorized to be appropriated to carry out this subchapter $15,000,000 for each of fiscal years 2007 through 2016, to remain available until expended.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="idca913cd5-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598" identifier="/us/usc/t43/s2408/b"><num value="b" class="bold">(b)</num><heading class="bold"> Rural water programs assessment</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Of the amounts made available under subsection (a), not more than $1,000,000 may be made available to carry out <ref href="/us/usc/t43/s2403">section 2403 of this title</ref> for each of fiscal years 2007 and 2008.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="idca913cd6-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598" identifier="/us/usc/t43/s2408/c"><num value="c" class="bold">(c)</num><heading class="bold"> Construction costs</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">No amounts made available under this section shall be used to pay construction costs associated with any rural water supply project.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<sourceCredit id="idca913cd7-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598">(<ref href="/us/pl/109/451/tI/s109">Pub. L. 109–451, title I, § 109</ref>, <date date="2006-12-22">Dec. 22, 2006</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/120/3356">120 Stat. 3356</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
